Kaya tapusin mo na ang ginagawa mo
at pumunta ka na rito.

874
00:49:00,334 --> 00:49:01,752
'Kay, pupunta ako diyan.'

875
00:49:01,835 --> 00:49:04,046
[nagliliyab na apoy]

876
00:49:04,129 --> 00:49:05,256
[tunog ng telepono]

877
00:49:05,881 --> 00:49:07,007
Hay! / Hay!

878
00:49:07,091 --> 00:49:08,425
Naku, ang swerte naman.

879
00:49:09,426 --> 00:49:10,469
KONEKTAONG TAWAG...
HEEJU

880
00:49:10,553 --> 00:49:13,556
[tunog ng telepono]

881
00:49:21,730 --> 00:49:23,732
Ah, teka.
Bakit hindi siya sumasagot?

882
00:49:23,816 --> 00:49:25,067
[tunog ng telepono]

883
00:49:36,287 --> 00:49:39,290
[♪ nakakapanabik na musika]

884
00:49:41,542 --> 00:49:42,918
[huminga nang palabas]

885
00:49:45,004 --> 00:49:48,007
[pagdagundong ng mga gulong]

886
00:50:01,312 --> 00:50:02,813
[huminga nang palabas]

887
00:50:02,896 --> 00:50:05,107
[mahinang sigaw]

888
00:50:05,190 --> 00:50:07,860
[nag-vibrate ang cellphone]

889
00:50:14,074 --> 00:50:16,035
[pag-ugong ng telepono]

890
00:50:25,669 --> 00:50:28,172
[Woogy] Kumusta? Uh, Heeju.
Nasaan ka?

891
00:50:28,255 --> 00:50:30,132
-Bakit hindi ka sumagot?
-[sigaw nang mahina]

892
00:50:30,215 --> 00:50:31,342
Nandoon ka?

893
00:50:31,425 --> 00:50:32,968
[Sigaw ni Heeju nang mahina]

894
00:50:33,052 --> 00:50:34,553
Naririnig mo ba ako?

895
00:50:34,637 --> 00:50:36,930
Hindi kita marinig.
Ano'ng sinasabi mo?

896
00:50:37,014 --> 00:50:38,849
[bumukas ang pinto]

897
00:50:38,932 --> 00:50:40,142
[Heeju bottom]

898
00:50:42,353 --> 00:50:43,937
Kawawang sanggol.

899
00:50:48,150 --> 00:50:50,110
Itinago mo ang mga gintong baras sa minahan,
hindi ba?

900
00:50:51,362 --> 00:50:53,822
[Yujin] Nakakita ako ng uling na natambak sa mga
gulong ng kotse.

901
00:50:54,657 --> 00:50:55,699
[Yujin] Dito.

902
00:50:55,783 --> 00:50:59,370
[Yujin] Ang minahan ng karbon sa dulo
ng National Route 7, tama ba?

903
00:50:59,453 --> 00:51:00,496
Sa loob ng agos.

904
00:51:00,579 --> 00:51:02,331
[Eugene] Ha? Ha?

905
00:51:02,414 --> 00:51:04,500
-Tama?
-Bb. Cha! Bb. Cha, sandali!

906
00:51:04,583 --> 00:51:05,751
Hindi mo sila mahahanap nang mag-isa.

907
00:51:05,834 --> 00:51:07,336
Ako lang ang nakakaalam
kung nasaan sila nang eksakto.

908
00:51:07,419 --> 00:51:08,504
Sasamahan kita!

909
00:51:08,587 --> 00:51:11,674
[Heeju] Pwede tayong magsama-sama
at hatiin ang mga gold bar, okay?

910
00:51:11,757 --> 00:51:13,384
Ngayon mo sinasabi 'yan?

911
00:51:13,467 --> 00:51:16,220
[Yujin] Huli na ang lahat.
Hindi kita kailangan.

912
00:51:16,303 --> 00:51:17,763
Titingnan ko buong gabi kung kinakailangan.

913
00:51:17,846 --> 00:51:19,598
Gagamit na lang ako ng metal detector
o kung ano pa man.

914
00:51:21,725 --> 00:51:23,352
Ang inosente mo talaga.

915
00:51:23,435 --> 00:51:25,813
Sa tingin mo ba talaga ay lagi kayong nandito ni Lee Dokyung?

916
00:51:25,896 --> 00:51:27,439
dahil mahalaga ka talaga?

917
00:51:27,523 --> 00:51:29,149
[Yujin] Parang nasabi ko na sa iyo.

918
00:51:29,233 --> 00:51:32,736
Ang tanging dahilan kung bakit ka naging kapaki-pakinabang
ay dahil sa ginto.

919
00:51:32,820 --> 00:51:33,946
Hindi dahil kailangan ka namin.

920
00:51:34,029 --> 00:51:35,239
-Nakikiusap ako sa iyo.
-[Yujin] Okay?

921
00:51:35,322 --> 00:51:36,407
[hininga]

922
00:51:36,490 --> 00:51:38,367
[Heeju] Hatiin natin sila!

923
00:51:38,951 --> 00:51:41,578
[Hinahabol ang hininga ni Heeju]

924
00:51:41,662 --> 00:51:42,705
[Umiiyak si Heeju]

925
00:51:42,788 --> 00:51:44,707
Pakiusap!

926
00:51:44,790 --> 00:51:46,583
[mahinang sigaw]

927
00:51:47,459 --> 00:51:51,547
[Yujin] Alam mo, iniisip ko kung ano
ang gagawin ko sa'yo.

928
00:51:51,630 --> 00:51:53,424
[Yujin] Medyo naguluhan ako.

929
00:51:53,507 --> 00:51:55,259
Pero tinulungan mo lang akong magdesisyon.

930
00:51:56,427 --> 00:51:59,722
Oo. Hindi karapat-dapat
sa ginto ang isang tulad mo.

931
00:51:59,805 --> 00:52:01,765
[mahinang sigaw]

932
00:52:01,849 --> 00:52:03,392
[bumukas at sumara ang pinto]

933
00:52:04,977 --> 00:52:05,978
[tunog ng pinto ng kotse]

934
00:52:07,604 --> 00:52:09,064
[bumaliktad ang makina ng kotse]

935
00:52:09,148 --> 00:52:10,774
[pag-ikot ng makina]

936
00:52:10,858 --> 00:52:13,068
[tumitik ang mga gulong]
ESTILO
::cue()

937
00:52:14,486 --> 00:52:16,238
[Yujin] Inumin mo lang ito
at huwag ka nang magigising.

938
00:52:17,781 --> 00:52:19,158
[Yujin] Akala mo umiibig ka,
pero ang totoo,

939
00:52:19,241 --> 00:52:20,868
Nakakainis ka kay Dokyung.

940
00:52:20,951 --> 00:52:23,120
At kahit na masira ang buhay mo,

941
00:52:23,203 --> 00:52:26,665
Isinisigaw mo pa rin,
"Nagmahal talaga ako." Tama ba?

942
00:52:26,749 --> 00:52:28,792
Buong buhay mo ay
sinasabi mo iyan sa sarili mo.

943
00:52:28,876 --> 00:52:31,044
[Humihingal si Heeju]

944
00:52:31,128 --> 00:52:32,838
[Yujin] Sinta.

945
00:52:33,756 --> 00:52:35,549
[Yujin] Gusto mo ba talagang magpatuloy sa
buhay nang ganyan?

946
00:52:35,632 --> 00:52:37,176
[Umungol si Heeju]

947
00:52:37,259 --> 00:52:38,719
Mamatay ka na lang.

948
00:52:39,928 --> 00:52:42,931
[mahinang sigaw]

949
00:52:45,726 --> 00:52:47,269
[pag-ubo]

950
00:52:47,352 --> 00:52:48,854
[kalabog ng bote]

951
00:52:48,937 --> 00:52:52,399
[parehong huminga nang malalim]

952
00:52:52,483 --> 00:52:54,359
Magandang gabi, sinta.

953
00:52:54,443 --> 00:52:56,195
Magpakailanman.

954
00:52:56,278 --> 00:52:59,281
[♪ nakakakabang musika]

955
00:53:02,701 --> 00:53:04,578
[pag-ubo]

956
00:53:12,419 --> 00:53:15,589
[Umungol si Heeju]

957
00:53:20,803 --> 00:53:22,471
[mahinang pag-ubo]

958
00:53:39,071 --> 00:53:40,489
[malakas na umuugong ang mga ilaw]

959
00:53:40,572 --> 00:53:43,283
[Umungol si Heeju]

960
00:54:07,266 --> 00:54:10,269
[patuloy ang ungol]

961
00:54:13,564 --> 00:54:16,567
[pag-ubo]

962
00:54:20,988 --> 00:54:23,448
[hinihingal]

963
00:54:23,532 --> 00:54:26,493
[hininga nang malalim]

964
00:54:26,577 --> 00:54:29,246
[langitngit ng pinto]

965
00:54:30,289 --> 00:54:33,292
[hirap huminga]

966
00:54:40,132 --> 00:54:42,134
[pag-ubo]

967
00:54:43,635 --> 00:54:46,638
[papalapit na ang sasakyan]

968
00:54:46,722 --> 00:54:47,931
[mga biro]

969
00:54:51,935 --> 00:54:53,562
[Woogy] Whoa! Heeju!

970
00:54:53,645 --> 00:54:54,896
Ikaw ba?

971
00:54:54,980 --> 00:54:56,273
Bumangon ka.

972
00:54:56,356 --> 00:54:57,858
Ayos ka lang?

973
00:54:59,735 --> 00:55:00,902
Saan ka pupunta?

974
00:55:00,986 --> 00:55:01,987
[hininga]

975
00:55:02,070 --> 00:55:03,322
[Woogy] Ha?

976
00:55:04,114 --> 00:55:05,866
-Kailangan ko nang pumunta.
-Saan ka pupunta?

977
00:55:05,949 --> 00:55:08,201
Ang minahan?
Dalhin natin ang kotse ko.

978
00:55:08,744 --> 00:55:11,288
-Hindi mo kaya. Huwag mo akong sundan.
-Ah, halika rito!

979
00:55:11,371 --> 00:55:14,374
[parehong ungol]

980
00:55:15,709 --> 00:55:17,544
- [Woogy] Okay.
-[Bumuntong hininga] Cha Yujin.

981
00:55:17,628 --> 00:55:20,631
[parehong ungol]

982
00:55:23,383 --> 00:55:25,802
[mga gintong baras na tumutunog]

983
00:55:25,886 --> 00:55:27,638
[umungol]

984
00:55:38,815 --> 00:55:39,983
Narinig ko lahat sa tawag.

985
00:55:40,067 --> 00:55:41,985
Ang babaeng 'yon, si Cha Yujin.

986
00:55:42,694 --> 00:55:44,071
Talagang nilamon
ka ng droga ng babaeng 'yon.

987
00:55:44,154 --> 00:55:46,198
[Woogy] At papunta siya sa minahan
para nakawin ang ginto.

988
00:55:46,948 --> 00:55:48,033
Bilisan mo.

989
00:55:49,076 --> 00:55:50,619
Malamang ay kinuha niya ang kotse niya.

990
00:55:52,287 --> 00:55:55,832
Kung aalis tayo ngayon,
makakarating tayo roon bago pa siya makarating.

991
00:55:55,916 --> 00:55:58,085
Ang kulit ni Cha Yujin.
ESTILO
::cue()

992
00:55:58,168 --> 00:56:01,630
[pag-ikot ng makina ng kotse]

993
00:56:01,713 --> 00:56:04,716
[mga ilaw na umuugong]

994
00:56:16,603 --> 00:56:17,604
[tumunog ang alarma ng kotse]

995
00:56:28,532 --> 00:56:29,908
[mga ungol]

996
00:56:29,991 --> 00:56:31,743
[bumukas ang pinto ng kotse]

997
00:56:31,827 --> 00:56:33,078
Ha?

998
00:56:33,161 --> 00:56:34,162
[sumarado ang pinto ng kotse]

999
00:56:35,539 --> 00:56:36,540
Cha Yujin?

1000
00:56:38,875 --> 00:56:39,876
Oo.

1001
00:56:41,169 --> 00:56:42,170
[tumatawa]

1002
00:56:44,548 --> 00:56:46,133
Nasaan ang kabaong?

1003
00:56:47,467 --> 00:56:48,468
Ha?

1004
00:56:51,138 --> 00:56:53,432
[Yujin] Uh, yung kabaong?

1005
00:56:58,520 --> 00:56:59,521
[ungol ni Yujin]

1006
00:56:59,604 --> 00:57:02,607
[parehong nahihirapan]

1007
00:57:02,691 --> 00:57:04,651
-[hinihingal]
- Putang ina!

1008
00:57:05,444 --> 00:57:07,529
Medyo naiinip na ako.

1009
00:57:07,612 --> 00:57:09,406
Kaya wala akong oras para makinig
sa mga dahilan mo.

1010
00:57:09,489 --> 00:57:11,032
Pasensya na po.

1011
00:57:11,116 --> 00:57:12,325
Magtatanong ako ulit.

1012
00:57:12,409 --> 00:57:15,287
[Humihingal si Yujin]

1013
00:57:15,370 --> 00:57:17,497
Nasaan ang ginto.

1014
00:57:17,581 --> 00:57:20,584
[Humihingal si Yujin]

1015
00:57:20,667 --> 00:57:23,545
Hindi! Hindi ko ninakaw!
Hindi ko-

1016
00:57:23,628 --> 00:57:25,464
-Ang kinuha ko-
-Talaga?

1017
00:57:25,547 --> 00:57:28,675
-[Umungol si Hocheol]
-[Hinahabol-hininga ni Yujin]

1018
00:57:37,851 --> 00:57:38,852
[Kang] Sagutin mo ang tawag na ito.

1019
00:57:45,025 --> 00:57:46,067
[mga ungol]

1020
00:57:49,446 --> 00:57:51,156
[huminga nang malalim]
Kumusta?

1021
00:57:51,239 --> 00:57:53,492
[Yujin] Do-Dokyung.

1022
00:57:53,575 --> 00:57:56,912
[Humihingal si Yujin]

1023
00:57:56,995 --> 00:57:58,163
Yujin.

1024
00:57:58,246 --> 00:57:59,623
Kapitan, ngayon na...

1025
00:58:00,957 --> 00:58:03,543
...malapit
nang huminga ang kasintahan mo.

1026
00:58:03,627 --> 00:58:06,338
Kung mabubuhay siya o mamamatay,
nakasalalay lahat sa iyo.

1027
00:58:06,421 --> 00:58:08,840
Nasaan ang kabaong?

1028
00:58:08,924 --> 00:58:10,425
[Napabuntong hininga si Yujin]

1029
00:58:10,509 --> 00:58:14,346
[Hocheol] Putang ina. Mas mabuting magsalita ka na.
Malapit na siyang mamatay.

1030
00:58:16,139 --> 00:58:18,308
[Sigaw ni Yujin]

1031
00:58:20,268 --> 00:58:21,770
Hindi ko alam.

1032
00:58:21,853 --> 00:58:25,273
[Yujin] Ang minahan! Ang minahan! Ang minahan!
Nasa minahan 'yan. May minahan.

1033
00:58:25,357 --> 00:58:26,817
[Hocheol] Aling minahan?

1034
00:58:26,900 --> 00:58:28,193
[Umungol si Hocheol]

1035
00:58:28,276 --> 00:58:29,569
[Yujin] Dito.

1036
00:58:29,653 --> 00:58:31,571
[Pabagu-bago ang paghinga ni Yujin]

1037
00:58:31,655 --> 00:58:33,698
[ubo]
[Yujin] Nandito.

1038
00:58:33,782 --> 00:58:36,451
[hininga nang malalim]

1039
00:58:36,535 --> 00:58:40,664
[Yujin] Kapag-kapag-kapag nakarating ka
na sa dulo ng National Route 7,

1040
00:58:40,747 --> 00:58:43,917
Sa pinakadulo ay ang drift number otso.

1041
00:58:44,000 --> 00:58:45,293
Doon na iyon.

1042
00:58:46,837 --> 00:58:48,547
[Yujin] Pasensya na!

1043
00:58:48,630 --> 00:58:51,424
Pasensya na! Sumusumpa ako na hindi ko ito ninakaw!
Pakiusap, hayaan mo akong mabuhay! Hindi!

1044
00:58:51,508 --> 00:58:53,635
Tumigil ka, hindi! Pakiusap, huwag!

1045
00:58:53,718 --> 00:58:57,389
[Humihingal si Yujin]

1046
00:58:57,472 --> 00:58:58,974
[parehong nahihirapan]

1047
00:58:59,057 --> 00:59:00,517
Yujin?

1048
00:59:00,600 --> 00:59:04,187
[Umungol si Hocheol]

1049
00:59:04,271 --> 00:59:06,731
[Napabuntong hininga si Yujin]

1050
00:59:15,198 --> 00:59:18,201
[Mabigat na huminga si Hocheol]

1051
00:59:24,541 --> 00:59:25,625
[tunog ng telepono]

1052
00:59:28,211 --> 00:59:29,212
Hoy.

1053
00:59:31,840 --> 00:59:33,508
[Dokyung] Heeju, ako ito, Dokyung.

1054
00:59:33,592 --> 00:59:34,885
Natuklasan ni Park ang tungkol sa mga gold bar.

1055
00:59:34,968 --> 00:59:36,386
Ilipat ang mga ito nang mabilis.

1056
00:59:41,266 --> 00:59:42,267
[tunog ng mga gintong bar]
ESTILO
::cue()

1057
00:59:58,033 --> 01:00:01,036
[umungol]

1058
01:00:02,871 --> 01:00:03,872
Tae. / Tae.

1059
01:00:03,955 --> 01:00:06,958
[mga bar na tumutunog]

1060
01:00:40,784 --> 01:00:43,787
[♪ dramatikong musika]

1061
01:00:50,919 --> 01:00:55,548
[Lalaking Mang-aawit] ♪ Panibagong araw panibagong oras ♪

1062
01:00:55,632 --> 01:00:59,928
♪ Malayang nahuhulog sa aking isipan ♪

1063
01:01:00,011 --> 01:01:07,018
♪ Hahanapin ko lahat ng dahilan
ng pag-alis ♪

1064
01:01:09,354 --> 01:01:14,442
♪ Kapag lahat ng tao sa paligid ko ay nagbabago ♪

1065
01:01:14,526 --> 01:01:18,905
♪ Lahat maliban sa akin ♪

1066
01:01:18,989 --> 01:01:23,326
♪ Lahat ng mga bagay na inakala kong kaya kong maging ♪

1067
01:01:24,411 --> 01:01:26,871
♪ Hindi maabot ♪

1068
01:01:28,790 --> 01:01:33,378
♪ Iiwan ko na ang lahat ♪

1069
